imdb.plot outline: The Angry Brothers Omaha Shock O Rama is a hosted horror movie anthology prorgram appearing on KPAO public access tv cox ch #22 in Omaha Nebraska. The show revolves around the hosts Brother Jack Angry and Brother James Angry a Pair of Monks (one zombie and one not ..uh for the moment that is) and thier crew of scantily clad dominatrixes (lady Torrid) , demons (Inferna, ash and Syn the devil sisters) and other characters. Brothers Jack and James Angry bring you the worst in grade b shlock horror and indie films, all the while working for "down below" but screwing it up more often than not.
